  m_text: Dragged to oblivion's brink, he found a flicker. Not mercy, but rage. A
    searing will rejected the Veil's embrace, tearing him back from true demise.
    Twisted, grotesquely changed, his form became a vessel for a burning vow. Vengeance,
    a crimson ember, ignited in the ruin of his soul.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
