  m_text: Behold, the realm of Aerthos, a world bathed in the ethereal glow of its
    celestial spheres, where the very air hummed with boundless vitality. From the
    ancient, towering structures that touched the clouds, guardians of forgotten
    epochs, to the verdant, sprawling landscapes teeming with vibrant, unique flora,
    life pulsed in every corner. Its cities, vibrant tapestries of light and sound,
    bustled with the joyful rhythm of daily existence, a testament to an age of unparalleled
    peace and prosperity. Here, every dawn brought forth a symphony of life, and
    every twilight painted skies of breathtaking, otherworldly beauty.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d76c4b9df01da4ed287ac895aaeaaf01, type: 2}
