--- !u!114 &173416372
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 173416369}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'From their own agony, the fallen angels perceived a flicker of defiance.
    His will, a raw ember, stood against the Veil. Recognizing this unique, corrupted
    strength, the celestial guardians, in their fading grace, descended. They offered
    not salvation, but purpose: a mask, born of ancient light, to seal his torment
    and forge his resolve. A new path, bathed in crimson, was laid bare.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d76c4b9df01da4ed287ac895aaeaaf01, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 6587870914143440735, guid: d76c4b9df01da4ed287ac895aaeaaf01, type: 2}
  m_fontSharedMaterials: []
