--- !u!114 &254294004
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 254294003}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 94ae4e61eddb94948884e6912c426d47, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  storyPanels:
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 1104600072}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1637026426}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 617383284}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 62867073}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f95af468c69f64b03a7f3a56eb5a0e9e, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dd8647eeba5e14b0cb826574e0e6a0c7, type: 3}
    panelText: Behold, the realm of Aerthos, a world bathed in the ethereal glow
      of its celestial spheres, where the very air hummed with boundless vitality.
      From the ancient, towering structures that touched the clouds, guardians of
      forgotten epochs, to the verdant, sprawling landscapes teeming with vibrant,
      unique flora, life pulsed in every corner. Its cities, vibrant tapestries of
      light and sound, bustled with the joyful rhythm of daily existence, a testament
      to an age of unparalleled peace and prosperity. Here, every dawn brought forth
      a symphony of life, and every twilight painted skies of breathtaking, otherworldly
      beauty.
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 1426236058}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1736157223}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 1322743888}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1541272155}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fca9da47c430841919e21865a0275b28, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dade2d069cf3d4493b777623d655e55b, type: 3}
    panelText: Among the countless souls of Aerthos, lived a man who knew no grand
      ambition, only the simple, profound joy of family. His world was his wife's
      gentle smile, the bright laughter of his young daughter, and the boundless
      energy of his elder son. Their humble home, nestled within the vibrant heart
      of the realm, was a sanctuary of warmth and love, where every day was a cherished
      moment, unaware of the encroaching darkness.
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 229595217}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 135240082}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 887354067}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1445871261}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 230240cb23be0432eb2edfea50f2df35, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c5d75889e15f743efa64e7f9d6f72fcc, type: 3}
    panelText: "The joy of Aerthos splintered. From abyssal chasms, the Abyssal Lord
      rose\u2014a titan of shadow and void. Its burning eyes unleashed a grotesque
      curse, a blight seeping into the world's very soul. Lands withered, life choked
      to silence. Aerthos wept, draped in the suffocating Veil of Decay. Desolation
      claimed all."
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 958301259}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1220146327}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 1723551105}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1080314233}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1ecd25d0a5f0644249f915673c172ec1, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c6251aac1cb0c4a23af7847064780506, type: 3}
    panelText: Beneath a bleeding moon, Aerthos fell. Sun a forgotten myth, replaced
      by unending twilight. Streets echoed with desperate steps, faces etched in
      despair. Corrupted halls of power declared twisted dominion. Hope, a flickering
      ember, died in the suffocating gloom of the Abyssal Lord's unending reign.
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 1455416416}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1151025734}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 660679095}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1541272155}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e2002d773c0a744069b68db60e7147ae, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 924d57e2be3454181a9523287a9cd5d3, type: 3}
    panelText: "Even the divine fell. Serphina, Azure, Aurelia \u2013 Aerthos's sacred
      guardians, their boundless light once shielding the realm. But the Abyssal
      Lord's curse defiled the heavens. Their radiant forms now flicker, powers dwindled
      to embers. Trapped, corrupted by the relentless Veil, they watch their world
      crumble, hope replaced by despair."
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 2004993151}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1211734097}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 870981232}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1191057395}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6ddba51db15f247538eafa8bd42e2d65, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8aa39a3ed8bf44ad79366053362b0796, type: 3}
    panelText: 'The Veil breached his sanctuary. He watched, helpless, as the curse
      seized his family: smiles turned to screams, laughter to cries, life to chilling
      stillness. Their forms dissolved into dust. A wound tore his soul. Then, the
      foul essence consumed him, flesh twisting, being warped, dragged into the same
      torment.'
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 53933687}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1638337077}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 602605673}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 1541272155}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1e8a9e3b3deeb4b148d11b18391a9a38, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f402c1b1088094f3bbb6ae0835bd2f26, type: 3}
    panelText: The Veil's breath claimed them all. He watched, powerless, as laughter
      turned to ash. Then, the curse found him. Flesh burned, bone twisted, his very
      form a canvas of agony. He was dragged to the precipice of oblivion, half-consumed,
      a mockery of what was.
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 677962968}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 843229084}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 974061604}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 10370071}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c386dbafe6d624648a0f171946e74c72, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ea94beeda1439415baf5a7bb233a9b32, type: 3}
    panelText: Dragged to oblivion's brink, he found a flicker. Not mercy, but rage.
      A searing will rejected the Veil's embrace, tearing him back from true demise.
      Twisted, grotesquely changed, his form became a vessel for a burning vow. Vengeance,
      a crimson ember, ignited in the ruin of his soul.
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 253088078}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 762951655}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 1617757471}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 173416372}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1fac7d976c1bc47a28d00ea7ca891cfc, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e237f5a870424d6a8982d4aa214fe4f, type: 3}
    panelText: 'From their own agony, the fallen angels perceived a flicker of defiance.
      His will, a raw ember, stood against the Veil. Recognizing this unique, corrupted
      strength, the celestial guardians, in their fading grace, descended. They offered
      not salvation, but purpose: a mask, born of ancient light, to seal his torment
      and forge his resolve. A new path, bathed in crimson, was laid bare.'
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  - panelRootUI: {fileID: 204155028}
    leftImageUI: {fileID: 1975137566}
    rightImageUI: {fileID: 967535786}
    panelTextUI: {fileID: 503564798}
    leftSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a046ebbc0e4274f1c9fe2a7d9e87d18e, type: 3}
    rightSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bfd352297f7694cb89651decfd1cfcad, type: 3}
    panelText: 'The mask, a crucible of anguish and rebirth, now forged his true
      form. No longer mere man, nor wholly consumed, he became the Veil-Touched,
      a beacon of vengeance against the encroaching blight. Guided by the fading
      light of the guardian angels, he embraced his twisted power. His path: reclamation.'
    panelFadeDuration: 1.5
    displayDuration: 5
  finalPanelRootUI: {fileID: 1134463211}
  finalImageUI: {fileID: 935903816}
  finalSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 833474598c0bc44ebb1e685600fedcd4, type: 3}
  continuePromptTextUI: {fileID: 967893585}
