      m_Calls: []
  m_text: Among the countless souls of Aerthos, lived a man who knew no grand ambition,
    only the simple, profound joy of family. His world was his wife's gentle smile,
    the bright laughter of his young daughter, and the boundless energy of his elder
    son. Their humble home, nestled within the vibrant heart of the realm, was a
    sanctuary of warmth and love, where every day was a cherished moment, unaware
    of the encroaching darkness.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d76c4b9df01da4ed287ac895aaeaaf01, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 6587870914143440735, guid: d76c4b9df01da4ed287ac895aaeaaf01, type: 2}
