  m_text: Aerthos, now a realm of ash and shadows. The Veil consumes, the Abyssal
    Lord reigns. But a flicker remains, a promise of retribution. For the fallen,
    for the lost, the Veil-Touched rises. His journey begins, into the heart of the
    curse.
